{"tid":1475097,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《電流戰爭》集結四大超級英雄？！蜘蛛俠，奇異博士，X-men,最後一位竟然是.....？","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T12:46:19.000Z","uid":209769,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e872fbe07e15ff2c940df8b5cf64850947e78ed","tid":1475097,"uid":209769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"《電流大戰》（英語：The Current War，中國大陸譯《電力之戰》，香港譯《電流戰爭》）是一部於2019年上映的美國傳記歷史電影，由艾方索&middot;戈梅茲-雷瓊執導，麥可&middot;米特尼克（英語：Michael Mitnick）編劇，並由班尼迪克&middot;康柏拜區、麥可&middot;夏儂、尼可拉斯&middot;霍特、凱薩琳&middot;華特斯頓與湯姆&middot;霍蘭德等人擔綱主演。該片講述湯瑪斯&middot;愛迪生（康柏拜區飾演）與喬治&middot;威斯汀豪斯（夏儂飾演）之間的「電流戰爭」。本片亦是康柏拜區與霍蘭德繼《復仇者聯盟4:終局之戰》後首部合作的電影。資料來源:維基百科<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z11kyCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz11kyCE.jpg&h=c74edfa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蜘蛛俠</span></strong></span> Tom Holland<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O86XASt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO86XASt.jpg&h=343de85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcxPrZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcxPrZg.jpg&h=48b6e0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">奇異博士</span></strong></span><br />\nBenedict Timothy Carlton Cumberbatch<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edaNdFG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedaNdFG.jpg&h=f29fe2a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJr8Hzx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJr8Hzx.jpg&h=f58ec118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">漢克&middot;麥考伊／野獸</span></span>Nicholas Caradoc Hoult<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DF1MufL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDF1MufL.jpg&h=c3b8cd97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ag37dJP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fag37dJP.jpg&h=939c62bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(以下防雷）<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n而最後一位是萬眾期待嘅...........<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">電神</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xM1if1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xM1if1.png&h=eb659f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZYOHK0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZYOHK0.jpg&h=c23c3463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謠傳漫威電影第四階段已無聲無息地拉開序幕，而這套《電流戰爭》其實是電神的起源電影，《電流戰爭》作為漫威電影第四階段頭炮，卻鮮為人知。相信亦是漫威方的宣傳手法，劇中透露大量有關第四階段未來走向，以及敵人。最後亦會曝光整個漫威<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">電影</span></strong></span>的起源，相信《電流戰爭》這套作為漫威電影第四階段頭炮，對剖釋整過漫威宇宙是不可或缺的，觀眾一定不能錯失這條關鍵鎖匙，定能為你解答漫威多年埋下的伏線。電影經已上畫，還不趕快支持？<br />\n利申：已三刷<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n最後，其實純玩笑。"},{"pid":"13e0db75f6fd17753ff6dc5e03de769ce3eafadf","tid":1475097,"uid":80567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"Tesla真係電神"},{"pid":"e6562877f28a417fe02aa6b9ade303de54c0c8f6","tid":1475097,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"睇左，好睇但唔夠喉"},{"pid":"cf3815e451259ed48a93c139d7908acb5d6d6f46","tid":1475097,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"反警黑嘅遊行要黑警批係咩玩法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"68afda68e896cf6f664dac2ad096d45fc867c7a5","tid":1475097,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"